Pretty fun game that I fully recommend. To list off some of its stand out features
-Great pixel art and art direction, locations always look either lived in or quite scenic;
-Great soundtrack with a good variety of themes;
-Good replay value and different paths you can take to complete the game;
-mastering the combat and movement feels great on Insane difficult;
-bosses are fun and diverse in play styles;
My play time reflects one run on Hard, one run on Insane, one Pacifist No Death run on Easy and some extra time dedicated to getting all the content in game.
